<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="but-conj">but <strong><em>conj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bət; bʌt/    美 /bət; bʌt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>但是；可是；而 (是)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>At the end of the day, we were tired but happy.
那天结束时，我们很累，但很快乐。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Excuse me</strong>, <strong>but</strong> may I use your phone?
对不起，我可以借用你的电话吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>除……外：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I had no other choice but to eat out.
我没有别的选择，只能在外面吃饭。</p><footer>2013 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I work not because I have to, <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ because I want to.  （2019 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. but  </p></div>